{"tid":766930,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【600億】庫德洛嘲諷中國軟弱　認為中國經濟遇到很大麻煩","createTime":"2018-08-04T05:00:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-06T01:26:30.000Z","uid":147314,"like":102,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"b1d4f121fd71af4219a25fc3ee84b541261d681b","tid":766930,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T05:00:07.000Z","msg":"庫德洛諷中國反制力度軟弱　警告別低估特朗普決心<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1410557_1_20180804003954.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1410557_1_20180804003954.jpg&h=e043cbe3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中美貿易戰升溫，中國決定採取反制措施，對第二批來自美國涉及約600億美元的商品，加徵5%至25%關稅，實施日期另行公布。<br />\n<br />\n美國白宮發言人桑德斯說，中國不應該採取報復行動，而是應該處理長期以來的不公平貿易行為。<br />\n<br />\n白宮經濟顧問庫德洛嘲諷，相對美國向2000億美元中國貨徵稅的規模，中方回應力度軟弱，認為中國經濟遇到很大麻煩。<br />\n<br />\n他警告中國，最好別低估特朗普總統再度出手的決心。<br />\n<br />\n庫德洛說，中國目前經濟情況糟糕，投資者正在撤離，人民幣匯率下跌，留意到日本股市較中國股市更有價格，這是他所樂見。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1410557-20180804.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1410557-20180804.htm&d=g5PjpyBZ77vyHVlMHyzzvdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=1229b503\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1410557-20180804.htm&h=bd3b9679\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1410557-20180804.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1068207f1bc3dedf8dc713dda32424bc6b51ee33","tid":766930,"uid":165377,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T05:06:57.000Z","msg":"老美上下一心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"771965c8e5d25b41685db022c29b0abe62c2370a","tid":766930,"uid":18012,"li